The '''Vishtu command enclave''' was the central building of the [[Vishtu Sector]], located on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] after the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] had terraformed the planet into Yuuzhan'tar. It contained the central offices of [[Prefect/Legends|Prefect]] [[Ash'ett]], as well as other high ranking [[Intendant caste|Intendants]]. The building was guarded by a [[swarbrik]] which, by the time the [[Priest caste|Priestess]] [[Ngaaluh]] came to investigate Ash'ett, was seriously ill, bleeding constantly&mdash;another failure of the [[World Brain]].

